Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00060606\bord0\pos(657.6,665)\frz42.56}木乃伊型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有这么多种类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的就是信封型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,凛用的是木乃伊型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天基本上都用这个
